    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "#4-91\nbaggage handbook\nSEE PGS. 3\n\u0026 5 FOR FREE BAGGAGE ALLOWANCE INFORMATION\nPAN AMERICAN",
      "BEFORE YOU GO . •\nANYTHING ELSE YOU'D LIKE TO KNOW?\nAlways feel free to take your questions on\nbaggage problems to the man who knows -\nyour Pan Am System representative. He'll\nsee to checking your baggage through to\nmost destinations even though it is to be trans-\nported over the routes of two or more carriers.\nThis will save you bother at connecting points.\nHe'll be glad to advise you ... as will anyone\nwearing the uniform of the airline that serves\nall six continents — Pan Am.\nPAN AMERICAN\nWORLD AIRWAYS SYSTEM\nPrinted in U.S.A.\nForm 9253-1426H\n3-63\n2012\n.19.0104"
    ],
